text: Haribhanga is a village situated in Salop Union of Ullahpara Upazila, Bangladesh. Nearby places are Mohonpur, Sheikhpara, Kansona, Salop, Gobindapur, Soguna, Gopalpur, Konabari, Kalipur, and Soratoil. ==References== Category:Populated places in Rajshahi Division Category:Villages in Sirajganj District Category:Villages in Rajshahi Division
